<p>
  <span class="nym">Ermentrude</span>
  <span class="gen">f.</span>
  
  <span class="etym"><span class="lang">Old High German</span> <i>ermen</i>, <span class="lang">Old Saxon</span> <i>irmin</i> 'strong' + <span class="lang">Proto-Germanic</span> <i>*þrūþ</i> 'strength' or <span class="lang">Proto-Germanic</span> <i>*trut</i> 'maiden'.
  </span>
  
</p>
  
<div class="usg">
  <p>The name of a 9th C queen of the Franks.</p>
</div>
  
  


